data.description: This is the one! Built in 2021, this nearly new home is move-in ready! Open concept living on the first floor. Spacious living room with adjoining well-equipped eat-in kitchen ft. island - perfect for entertaining! Dining area, first floor powder room! Flex room could be used as office, exercise room, craft room, bedroom - so many possibilities! Primary owner's suite with walk-in closet and adjoining bath ft. double vanity, shower. Large closets in additional bedrooms. Ultra-convenient 2nd floor laundry! All appliances stay, including the brand new dishwasher! Mechanicals, windows and roof only 3 years old = peace of mind! Convenient location close to just about everything in town. Don't miss this opportunity to call this house your home - schedule a showing today!
